product_name: Benefit CosmeticsRoller Lash Curling & Lifting Mascara
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsSustainable PackagingBenefit Cosmetics' Roller Lash Curling & Lifting Mascara with its eye-opening Hook 'n' Roll brush grabs, separates, lifts and curls while the instant curve-setting formula holds for 12 hours.
details: DetailsBenefitsWater-resistantClump-freeKey IngredientsContains Provitamin B5 & Serin, ingredients known for their lash-conditioning benefitsResearch Results97% said it visibly lifts lashes*87% said it gives long-lasting curl*94% said eyes look more wide open**Consumer panel survey on 31 women after 4 weeks.Item 2285068How To UseGently wiggle the wand from base of lashes to tip. Repeat across your lashline, making sure to catch every lash.Beauty tip: For super curl AND length, apply Roller Lash first to curl and lift your lashes then layer They're Real! Lengthening Mascara on top. It's sexy drama beyond belief!IngredientsAqua (Water), Paraffin, Polybutene, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Bis-Diglyceryl Polyacyladipate-2, Palmitic Acid, Stearic Acid, Vp/Eicosene Copolymer, Acacia Senegal Gum, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax, Aminomethyl Propanediol, 1,2-Hexanediol, Caprylyl Glycol, Silica, Candelilla Cera (Euphorbia Cerifera (Candelilla) Wax), Hydroxyethylcellulose, Panthenol, Butylene Glycol, Hydroxyacetophenone, Chlorphenesin, Pentylene Glycol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Algin, Serine, Disodium Phosphate, Sodium Phosphate, Polysorbate 60. May Contan: CI 77499 (Iron Oxides). No. 16347.Disclaimer: Product ingredient listings are updated periodically. Before using a Benefit product, please read the ingredient list on the packaging of your product to be sure that the ingredients are appropriate for your personal use.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Gently wiggle the wand from base of lashes to tip. Repeat across your lashline, making sure to catch every lash.Beauty tip: For super curl AND length, apply Roller Lash first to curl and lift your lashes then layer They're Real! Lengthening Mascara on top. It's sexy drama beyond belief!

reviews.headline: Love the brush
reviews.comments: Being older I have lost eyelashes. I have tried numerous mascaras looking for an answer. This brush allowed me to coat and separate my lashes so they look fuller. I will definitely keep using this mascara.

reviews.headline: THE QUALITY OF THE WAND IS VERY POOR.
reviews.comments:
I LOVE THIS MASCARA, HOWEVER THIS IS THE 2ND TIME THE BRUSH PART OF THE WAND HAS BROKEN OFF.

I WOULD NOT RECOMEND TO A FRIEND FOR THAT REASON BUT I WILL CONTINUE TO BUY IT BECAUSE I DO LOVE THE MASCARA.

reviews.headline: Gold Standard for Beautiful Lashes
reviews.comments: A friend at work told me about this, and I use it every day. My absolute favorite. And it doesn't leave raccoon eyes!

reviews.headline: The absolute best mascara ever!!
reviews.comments: I love this mascara so much!  I started wearing it about a year ago and I can definitely say that it is a great formula that sticks to your lashes all day! The wand is amazing and always gets all of my lashes! It is not clumpy at all and great at separating lashes! I love the volume that it gives my lashes! I wear it when I work out and it doesn't flake off of my lashes or smear on my face. I even wear it swimming. Over all the best mascara ever!!!!

reviews.headline: I would but this product again
reviews.comments: Great lengthening and long lasting mascara

reviews.headline: Best mascara ever. Easy to apply not chunky or too thick. Th
reviews.comments: Best mascara I have found. Not clumpy or too thick. Easy and will take less time to apply. Very smooth and stays on.

reviews.headline: Best mascara so far
reviews.comments: I had ordered a mascara that had top reviews and first time applying, it was thick and gooey that my eyelashes clumped together in one big mess!  I returned and bought this one. I had trialed the travel size and loved it.  The wand puts just enough product on lashes and separates them beautifully.  Doesn't smear all day and comes easily at night with remover.  Found my forever mascara!!!

reviews.headline: Its good but not worth the price
reviews.comments: I loooove that it doesnt clump at all. Seperates the lashes nicely. Doesnt give much length. If you can get it on sale its worth it.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again
reviews.comments: I like this product it one of the better mascara that I use.

reviews.headline: Don't Bother Wasting Your Money!
reviews.comments:
This is the worst product ever, and we're talking worse than BadGal by Benefit. It did absolutely nothing to improve my lashes whatsoever. I tried three different attempts to give this product a chance.

First, I applied only bare lashes. First coat was left eye from top and bottom lash was a nightmare to apply. It wasn't one simple swoop from root to tip. I had to really dig the brush into my eyelash line. It was a struggle, too much IMO. I did the same thing to the upper and lower lash. Took too long. Second, took double the time and spider eyes. Third, AHS on AMC. I'm going back to Roller Lash and returning this trash.

reviews.headline: Easy
reviews.comments: Gives an easy sweet lashe . Very little clumping but it selerates like it says . I wasent lookingbfir kength just a natural curl with non faje coverage , and tgats what it returns .

reviews.headline: Good mascara
reviews.comments: I bought it during the 21 days of beauty and because of the curved brush. I like it enough to pay half the price for it but not full price.

reviews.headline: Incredible
reviews.comments:
Ive seen this mascara around for years and always heard good reviews about it, but up until recently I was a loyal user to another mascara. So finally, I decided to try this one out when Ulta had a sale on mascaras. I bought several from different brands. Ultimately, this mascara (and one from another brand) stuck out to me the mostâ€¦ I was amazed at the length this mascara brought to my lashes. And it gives your lashes a good curl too. All these results with 1 coat !! So you really dont need to use a lot of product, or you can risk your lashes looking "spider-y."
It doesnt give you that dramatic, bold, intense eye look but more so the cheeky, cute, flirty everyday look. 
So this mascara has officially entered into my rotation for now as my everyday, daytime mascara and the other brand (Anastasia) as my nighttime mascara. 
Definitely try this product out and you'll be amazed!!

reviews.headline: Doesn't clump
reviews.comments: I don't want to say that it doesn't clump AT ALL. You need to run the wand along the edge of the container to get the goop off--but of all the mascaras I've tried, this is the only one I have bought twice!

reviews.headline: All time FAV
reviews.comments:
Comes in clutch when you want a glamorous look without clusters of strips. Definitely my go to! 
Get it girl!

reviews.headline: My stand by
reviews.comments: I have tried other mascara and always come back to this one, love it.

reviews.headline: PANDA EYES!!!
reviews.comments: I have used other benefit and they were great. This one, however; was the worst one yet. It was very watery and took forever to dry. If your eyes water the slightest bit Panda eyes are sure to come. Save your money. one use and to the trash it goes.

reviews.headline: Used to love
reviews.comments: I used to use this prodyct years ago and loved it but i purchased it again recently and started noticing it would started to flake and smudge on my under eye (i dont put mascara there) and when i used a different mascara that issue was gone, so the formula must not be that good anymore, don't recommend if you dont want raccoon eyes

reviews.headline: One of the worst mascara I've owned
reviews.comments: I'm so glad I didn't pay full price for this. I have straight lashes and this doesn't do anything as far as curling them. In addition I can't put this on my lower lashes because it automatically runs and I end up with the panda look  This is so disappointing. The Maneater by Tarte is way better.

reviews.headline: Ok, but wouldn't recommend
reviews.comments: This product gave me a good curl on my lashes, but at school always looking up and down this caused the mascara to leave black under and over my eyes overall would not recommend this product to someone who is constantly looking up and down
